notes.title: This is a Title
notes.body: this note was taken on 08/03/2023. I am attempting to create plutonium in my laboratory. I want it to be magical. I hope that it is cool enough to go into human history textbooks. Do you think the internet will be recoverable one day after all goes away in 1 billion years? Yeah... me either. Anyway, ciao for now.

notes.title: A Good Day
notes.body: Today is a good day. I think that this note will be added to the JSON server and I will have made more progress towards this case study project. I have not yet added any CSS so the way it looks is quite honestly... an eye sore and wow it would be silly to keep it like this. Once this works, I'm going to take a nice time to add some CSS to make this nicer to look at. It kind of feels like spring cleaning. Like progress has been made but you never really took the time to sit down and organize and deep clean everything. so... here it goes I suppose. Cheers! <3

notes.title: Hello World!
notes.body: Ink my whole body I don't get a silly quack. Did you put that on? Ummmmm... *sigh* *yawn* *scratch* I'm looking into buying a four-plex as a real estate investment opportunity... BUT I would rather win the lottery this Friday. It's overheating. It's like a nuclear reacter in there.

notes.title: Tacos Yum
notes.body: I like tacos and they are good. I like my tacos best with flour and cheese. Kind of like a cheesy roll up. A queso conjunction that was always meant to be. The southern peanut butter and jelly. Yes. It is very good and I do be enjoying it. I am EDITING THIS YAY. Tacos are good and nice
